# The cross-witness pattern moves from "research-mutawatir at L3 ceiling
# 0.85" (facts/14 + facts/18) to "research-mutawatir + L0 mathematical
# anchor + L1 precondition-verification" — a multi-stratum joint that
# composes per mizaj 11 + 14 to ABOVE the single-stratum L3 ceiling.
# Specifically: facts/14 provides 9+ research groups (~0.85), Condorcet
